kground-color:02af8a">2019 - 2020</h3> <img class="projectDetailImage1" src="assets/images/Poster2.jpg"> <p class="projectDetailImage1Caption">Poster Short Film Anushaasan designed<br>by Deepak Chakravarty for InDreamz<br>Motion Picture</p> <p class="projectDetailText" style="margin: 0; padding: 25px; text-align: justify">Anushaasan is a short film under production by InDreamz Motion Pictures however the project halt due to COVID-19. The film is based short story written by Deepak Chakravarty as an initiative to set-up environment for value based filmmaking in native town. It is very first step in Sawai Madhopur region towards its development into Film City led by InDreamz Motion Pictures®.<br><br>The film's mahurat shot was innaugrated by film <b><i>Pataakha</i></b> fame writer Mr Charan Singh 'Pathik' as Chief Guest, Hon. ADJ Mrs. Rekha Chaudhary as Guest of Honour and Mr. Shariq Naqwi, HoD Direction department GKFTII (T-Series) as Special Guest in presence of remaining Dignatories, Actors and Guests present at the event.<br><br>The event brought honour to a small city and made its citizen proud which is recognised as historical event in region by mainstream print media operating in the region. <a href="m5d9aC15v5r1g5A14u19h1a19a14.php"><button style="background-color: 02af8a; padding: 5px; border: none; border-radius: 5px; color: white; cursor: pointer">Media Coverage</button></a></p></div> <div class="projectDetail" id="projectDetailMSK"> <h3 class="ProjectsDetailSubHeading" style="background-color:02af8a">2018 - 2020</h3><a href="https://www.imdb.com/title/tt12211966/?ref_=tt_ch" target="_blank"><img class="projectDetailImage1" src="assets/images/Poster1.jpg"></a><p class="projectDetailImage1Caption">Poster Mohabbat Sitaaron Ki®</p> <p class="projectDetailText" style="margin: 0; padding: 25px; text-align: justify">Mohabbat Sitaaron Ki is first ever series of its kind in the world that takes you to the depth of love, passion and challenge that celebrities (Cinema, TV, Sports, Politics etc.) takes on to win heart of their Soulmate. <br><br> It has seven segments. The show is conceptualised, written, designed by Deepak Chakravarty. The pilot episode is directed and produced by Deepak Chakravarty soon after passing out from film school as an initiative to build career in Media Industry. Bollywood fame Actor Dharmendra Jacky Ladhani is associated with the project as an Host and Executive Producer. The project is listed on <a href="https://www.imdb.com/title/tt12211966/?ref_=tt_ch" target="_blank" style="color:blue; text-decoration:none">IMDb</a>. <a href="m5d9aC15v5r1g5M19K.php"><button style="background-color: 02af8a; padding: 5px; border: none; border-radius: 5px; color: white; cursor: pointer">Media Coverage</button></a></p></div><div class="projectDetail"><h3 class="ProjectsDetailSubHeading" style="background-color:02af8a" id="rilsProjectDescription">2019</h3><img class="projectDetailImage1" src="assets/images/logo3.png"><p class="projectDetailImage1Caption">Brand Image: Ranthambore International Literary Society™ (RILS).</p> <p class="projectDetailText" style="margin: 0; padding: 20px; text-align: justify">Ranthambore Int. Literary Society™ (RILS) is a nonprofit organisation founded in 2020 in Sawai Madhopur a heritage city of Rajasthan with a vision to inculcate quality literature reading & writing habit in regional masses. RILS by means of various proposed online education programmes is committed to nurture and empower the litteratuers and critics laying foundation for value based quality content production in region.<br><br>The mission of society is to build inter-network between existing writers in the region thereafter connecting them to worldwide network of quality litteratuers thus exposing them to international standards of literary writings. Creating bookeh of opportunities to gain woldwide acceptance to their writings by organising International Literary Festivals or Events facilitating the exchange of literary culture amoung the litteratuers accessing events and our website all over the world thus contributing unity in diversity through Literary Art.</p> <!-- © Copyright 2020 Deepak Chakravarty All rights Reserved --> </div> <div class="projectDetail"> <h3 class="ProjectsDetailSubHeading" id="RIFSprojectDescription" style="background-color:02af8a">2018</h3> <a href="https://youtu.be/uHDici0zdt8" target="_blank"><img class="projectDetailImage1" src="assets/images/logo1.gif"></a> <p class="projectDetailImage1Caption" style="padding: 25px">Brand Image: Ranthambore Int. Film Society® (RIFS).</p> <p class="projectDetailText" style="margin: 0; padding: 0 20px; text-align: justify">Ranthambore International Film Society® (RIFS) founded in Sawai Madhopur a heritage city in Rajasthan with a mission to promote tne quality cinema, improving standards of regional cinema, nuture Film/ Media Content Producers & Enterprenuers by conducting training and workshops in order to set up film/content production environment in the region. Conducting International film festivals and content bazar seminars and conferences in near future is another visionary step in setting up film/ content production environment. <br><br>Going by its vision RIFS has succesfully conducted first <a href="https://www.facebook.com/865430713788255/posts/910534085944584/?sfnsn=scwspmo"target="_blank"  style="color:blue; text-decoration:none">Acting Workshop</a> and supporting the production first short film in the region.</p></div> <div class="projectDetail"><h3 class="ProjectsDetailSubHeading" id="indreamzProjectDescription" style="background-color:02af8a">2017</h3><a href="https://ipindiaonline.gov.in/tmrpublicsearch/tmsearch.aspx?tn=161592818&st=Wordmark"target="_blank"><img class="projectDetailImage1" src="assets/images/logo5.png"></a> <p class="projectDetailImage1Caption">Brand Image: InDreamz Production®</p><p class="projectDetailText" style="margin: 0; padding: 25px; text-align: justify">InDreamz Production® is a film/content production unit started in small town by Deepak Chakravarty on footstep of Sandeep Marwah founder Film City Noida as a contribution in attempts to distribute the Hindi Film/Content production industry through out the country outside Mumbai especially northern region of India. The project is much focused on benefiting least privileged semi-urban and rural aspirants and passionates in field of literature and value based content writing and production.Thus the project started with a noble thought to enable these aspirants to identify their own intellectual property further empowering them to utilise the same to improve their living standard.</p></div></div></div> <?php require_once("includes/F15o20e18.php"); ?> </body> </html> <!-- © Copyright 2020 Deepak Chakravarty All rights Reserved -->